  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large tagine over low heat.",
    "Add the crushed garlic and sauté for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the Cheonggukjang, thyme, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Stir in the labneh cheese, if using.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with a sprinkle of thyme."
